Title: Dzialalnosc Zgromadzenia Salezjanskiego na plaszczyznie wychowania ku wartosciom moralnym i spolecznym/The Mission of the Salesian Congregation in the Light of Formation of Moral and Social Values
Abstract: This article portrays the most important elements of the Salesian formation and education in the context of
social life. It also points out the specifics of the community and its charism which set the foundations for this
congregation. The conclusion is a reflection on the key elements of the Salesian mission in the present world.   
Keywords: Salesians, Social Values, Moral Values
